{"tid":959530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【撞船封航道】數百人滯留郵輪碼頭 內地團︰無合理賠償會有行動","createTime":"2018-12-28T16:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T02:45:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0790238a5b92044a7b1d31b8d2a68ae4aea93ce0","tid":959530,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"星夢郵輪一艘郵輪「世界夢號」，原定今日傍晚6時許由啟德郵輪碼頭出發前往南沙，多個旅行團共數百人在離境大堂辦理手續等候上船，其間職員指南沙港發生撞船事故，船道封閉，「世界夢號」未能抵港接載乘客。<br />\n據讀者報稱，船公司指明日凌晨1時或能安排「世界夢號」抵港，惟未能確定。現場有不少人鼓譟，有人更指「飢寒交迫，無了期等待」，更有內地團友揚言如沒有合理賠償，將會有進一步行動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yt9QE53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYt9QE53.png&h=fcf48d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ranF2jq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FranF2jq.png&h=ca686c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181228/59081808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59081808&d=Y9q9H8tEEN%2FvhzvyBzNJMNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=eea902ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59081808&h=e3524a25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181228/59081808</a>"},{"pid":"694af38a3b5d76c37f89beecec4080ff02d29393","tid":959530,"uid":168366,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"坐22巴士去九龍城再返黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f3ee6338072f82259c83a1fe36ddb6d6b8708e","tid":959530,"uid":4964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中..."},{"pid":"6ba251ff8648b80b94c1432b897acae8b19fe36c","tid":959530,"uid":10757,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:12:56